{"title": "Beijing lambasts Nato over move to include China in future threat assessments", "tags": "world", "timestamp": "2022-04-08", "content": "LONDON - Chinese diplomats have lashed out at a statement from Nato, the United States-led military alliance in Europe, which accused Beijing of supporting the Russian invasion of Ukraine and vowed to include China in Nato's future threat assessments.\nAfter a meeting of Nato foreign ministers this week, Mr Jens Stoltenberg, the alliance's secretary-general, claimed that Beijing has \"chosen\" to support the Russian justification for the invasion of Ukraine."}